# mattermost webrtc video call plugin

Link: https://github.com/niklabh/mattermost-plugin-webrtc-video

## Usage

- Upload plugin via admin console and enable it.

- Ask a friend to do the same

- Go to any online user dm.

- Click on the video icon on the top right to start the call

- Give permission to video and audio.

- Accept call from friend side.
